rim width spec of >5" or 5.5" IIRC.

Any thoughts on this apparent mismatch and whether it's safe to go
with the wider-rim tire on splitty rims?

I'm going to replace my tranny, so I could also go with the Freeway
flier, but I thought I'd inquire as to your experiences.

